{"tid":786724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普「教訓」土耳其       陶傑：將會重建世界新格局","createTime":"2018-08-20T06:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T10:17:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c5dad964b55ec5169def36ad1b59c2838c502b98","tid":786724,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"2016年有一架俄羅斯戰機，在土耳其被撃落，發生戰機撃落事件，一度令普京和埃爾多安十分緊張，要敵對，西方正中下懷，但普京忍手，因為他有伊朗盟友，不想得失土耳其，普京主動向埃爾多安示好，而埃爾多安就撃落戰機一事，向俄羅斯道歉，雙方很快重修於好，美國就不滿，不舒服，果然俄羅斯要買武器給土耳其，離間計在某程度上成功了。<br />\n<br />\n美國利用土耳其一個住在費城，反對派流亡領袖，在土耳其策動政變，兩年前一場政變被埃爾多安強力鎮壓，不但鎮壓還拘捕很多人，而且把國內數以千計的法官、高級官員、政府教師、傳媒主管全部解僱，很多人投入監獄，他要不止一黨獨大，而且一人專制。<br />\n<br />\n這時特朗普發現埃爾多安養不熟，既然養不熟就無謂客客氣氣，索性遇佛殺佛，撕破臉皮，於是增加五成入口關稅，埃爾多安就說退出美元貨幣聯盟，和人民幣，和俄國、中國的交易，這方面在美國政府估算之中，他分分鐘向土耳其實施制裁，因為土耳其里拉幣值，七個月內跌近百分之三十五，美國一如所料幣值一直弱化，變成阿根廷。<br />\n<br />\n埃爾多安上台廢總理職位，一個總統獨大，類似明朝朱元璋廢宰相制，既然如此你治國無方，國民經濟破敗，金融體制崩潰，萬民憤恨指向他一個，所以特朗普豪賭，會有人沽棋子、股市得利，長遠來說要教訓土耳其，不惜令土耳其脫離歐洲，甚至北約陣營，此做法改寫世界秩序，掃場，重新創造世界新格局大手筆，至於有多成功，就要看特朗普可否連任，如果他十一月中期大選大勝，可以連任的話，八年有足夠時間讓他成為第二任列根，比列根捍衛民主自由的功績猶有過之。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180819/615095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180819%2F615095&d=ijgpc%2BAPKghHsf2yIHXsNJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ac434644\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180819%2F615095&h=72e9df65\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180819/615095</a>"},{"pid":"94da9c18b7cfb9f9f3f1437f8e964f4ff5e44704","tid":786724,"uid":26752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:54:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">In 侵 we trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f6775d31c13f7fabb99f578f8802f806cff6b5a4","tid":786724,"uid":2429,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"比列根捍衛民主自由的功績猶有過之<br />\n<br />\n打贏新冷戰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006aae7b65cec5bc937c8ddd3200c39259608070","tid":786724,"uid":89857,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"有生之年...希望可以睇到中共解體"},{"pid":"1e446338fe043622006854c6f49424ebe970384f","tid":786724,"uid":4392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:18:04.000Z","msg":"美國有冇民調顯示trump trump 有幾成機會呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505c80a4e5e5ebcef41bdf904a5543ed4663a9ed","tid":786724,"uid":44163,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"據非正式統計<br />\n香港最少有8成人唔識分買同賣呢兩隻字"},{"pid":"27735f67e3ca5c9dd0e63855b86a04edde635bad","tid":786724,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e446338fe043622006854c6f49424ebe970384f","tid":786724,"uid":4392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:18:04.000Z","msg":"美國有冇民調顯示trump trump 有幾成機會呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"仲要信民調？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8853cddb44a800c27ba03fc739d5e74621ab813","tid":786724,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e446338fe043622006854c6f49424ebe970384f","tid":786724,"uid":4392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:18:04.000Z","msg":"美國有冇民調顯示trump trump 有幾成機會呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"幾天前看過民調，眾議院死硬，參議院保大多數只55波，洲長輸好多"},{"pid":"f6066a4d9bc3e23ce0a261c288dac763c54a8b8e","tid":786724,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"美國俄亥俄州舉行眾議院席位補選，點票將近完成，共和黨宣布其參選人已經勝出，但傳媒報道民主黨參選人僅以近1,700票落後，需等待最終點票結果才能分勝負。俄州製造業人口為全國第三多，但共和黨在今次補選表現遠遜預期，外界認為結果或反映民主黨能在中期選舉佔優。<br />\n<br />\n初步點票結果顯示，共和黨參選人鮑爾德森（Troy Balderson）取得50.1%選票，民主黨參選人奧康納（Danny O'Connor）則取得49.3%選票，兩者相差不足1%，但共和黨已提早宣布勝選，總統特朗普亦在Twitter恭賀鮑爾德森。<br />\n<br />\n但傳媒報道，目前仍有約8,000張選票等待點算，足以左右大局，因此暫未能斷言誰人勝出。若2人票數差距不足0.5%，就要重新點票。<br />\n<br />\n這次補選被視為特朗普施政的成績表，預示11月中期選舉的形勢。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普2016年競選總統時，在該州得票以11%佔優，共和黨眾議院代表蒂貝里（Pat Tiberi）更以37%壓倒性勝出。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，即使鮑爾德森最終勝出，優勢都比2016年選舉時大幅收窄，反映民主黨11月中期選舉時較有優勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2133254/美國製造業重鎮俄亥俄州補選%20共和黨支持度大跌\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2133254%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E9%87%8D%E9%8E%AE%E4%BF%84%E4%BA%A5%E4%BF%84%E5%B7%9E%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8%2520%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C&d=ijgpc%2BAPKghHsf2yIHXsNJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c596efe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2133254/美國製造業重鎮俄亥俄州補選%20共和黨支持度大跌</a>"},{"pid":"03cc144e1aac7a995b4f65ac1883399b2e18d0fe","tid":786724,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"不需一兵就打殘個國家,,中共小撚心"},{"pid":"2d3f64a84e9a08c940a5caf6e61cf1f4aa8a086b","tid":786724,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉就係最好嘅例子"},{"pid":"b93026b69910dbb2c07213d762ab91e856153784","tid":786724,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c71dfc6c5319e7db3ba14e1863fcf07849a465","tid":786724,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"美國駐土耳其大使館被槍擊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bwgAcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bwgAcS</a>"},{"pid":"14eebcf8f94af6786c07b518d4ff91870598967d","tid":786724,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:08:00.000Z","msg":"神人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe47aa6ef8f10ad9785cec5945b5018af148c2ff","tid":786724,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}